{"tid":864382,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人幾時先識咩叫環保？","createTime":"2018-10-16T07:11:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-16T17:00:19.000Z","uid":146923,"like":155,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"38a9461d971bdf4be3c45c453811e72f7be28c59","tid":864382,"uid":146923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T07:11:10.000Z","msg":"班撚樣開口埋口要「環保」，究竟有冇諗過乜嘢先係環保，乜嘢係多鳩餘？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1. 無飲管日<br />\n<br />\n市面上好多餐廳都開始有樣學樣 搞埋曬啲咩無飲管日 先唔講凍飲啲冰下下頂到牙都僵 有幾多餐廳會將個杯洗乾淨？冇飲管要同我杯零距離接觸 上一手啲污跡仲要殘留係上面 變相同幾十人間接kiss 核突過奶廁板<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  啲人嫌污糟就會拿多幾張紙巾抹個杯嘴 果幾張紙巾咪又係浪費翻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2. 走餐盤墊<br />\n<br />\n比較常出現係大學canteen 好撚興餐盤唔用紙墊住<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啲凍飲杯本身濕 冇盤墊嘅磨擦好易跣 係canteen食飯見過無數人打瀉左成個餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  呢啲唔係浪費？倒瀉完又係要鋪一大疊紙巾索翻乾撻地 又要勞煩清潔姐姐幫手拖地 為嘅就係慳果一張濕鳩餐紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n條數仲未計完，當你打瀉左個燒味飯加紅豆冰 啲原材料係咪要靠養豬、雞、牛得翻嚟？畜牧業本身係暖化來源之一，啲農畜排便會釋放甲烷，係一種比二氧化碳更加有害嘅氣體。原材料採集完，係咪要用車運過去工廠加工再運過嚟餐廳賣比你班撚樣食？呢part排放出嘅汽車廢氣你考慮左未？加工過程造成嘅污染你考慮左未？你慳左一張盤墊，下一秒咪又係第二方面浪費翻轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3. 外賣自取時自備餐盒<br />\n<br />\n呢樣都算on9之最<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  餐廳本身有自己嘅碟、杯，嘢食嘢飲嘅份量係咁多就咁多 出餐份量會有自己標準 啲嘢食要裝到幾滿 啲嘢飲裝到個杯邊個位等等 而你條濕鳩so-called環保人士就一嘢隊個大樽比人裝嘢飲 人地要點預比你 一杯奶茶350ml 你拿個1L樽嚟係咪想人裝1L奶茶比你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有啲餐廳會預先斟定 你隊個樽比人人地咪用原本個杯倒翻落你個樽到 如果係即棄杯就直接丟棄 重用嘅又要洗 啲洗潔精仲要比原本用多一倍 因為你自己個樽用完都要洗呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你以為對環境有害嘅淨係得果幾個濕鳩膠袋同濕鳩飲筒？<br />\n<br />\n總結：呢班撚屌淨係考慮到自己雙眼睇到嘅嘢，但就完全忽視左背後衍生嘅其他後果，計我話呢班人死撚左佢對地球就最撚環保。"},{"pid":"fca8c253f308e353dc9f0c1954fcb5a6a0ed1b6e","tid":864382,"uid":48362,"like":44,"dislike":3,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T07:15:44.000Z","msg":"環保人士要人道毀滅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6750af26137be43a83cc6a29dfb0b2ca708a848","tid":864382,"uid":146923,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"quote":{"pid":"fca8c253f308e353dc9f0c1954fcb5a6a0ed1b6e","tid":864382,"uid":48362,"like":44,"dislike":3,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T07:15:44.000Z","msg":"環保人士要人道毀滅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T07:23:20.000Z","msg":"環保本身係一個好嘅慨念，但唔係你求鳩其整個無飲管日就舒緩到，一個政策potentially會衍生出嚟嘅後果係好重要，而班撚屌往往忽略左呢點 一味追求自我感覺良好嘅 fake highs<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bda679181c2e82ad4f9824208d5e209ab31555dc","tid":864382,"uid":17866,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T07:40:46.000Z","msg":"好公道既<br />\n佢地敢正視中國對環境破壞，自己office 較高番過25.5，去抗議我咪無飲管日"},{"pid":"3e444cb506a2affc72731fbbbb691e9d50e68d89","tid":864382,"uid":23707,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T07:42:11.000Z","msg":"無嘢dom落垃圾筒=環保"},{"pid":"0f047f34af7cf1a20369dca20ddb3fb07ba69083","tid":864382,"uid":146923,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"bda679181c2e82ad4f9824208d5e209ab31555dc","tid":864382,"uid":17866,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T07:40:46.000Z","msg":"好公道既<br />\n佢地敢正視中國對環境破壞，自己office 較高番過25.5，去抗議我咪無飲管日"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T07:47:36.000Z","msg":"陣間熱到中暑點支持環保呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66364737951a3188d02f5a720ae69fcd2fdcfd23","tid":864382,"uid":129235,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T07:48:56.000Z","msg":"樓主高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  正評<br />\n<br />\n留意一樣野，你講既3個例子全部都包含左2個步驟<br />\n<br />\n一係先評估 用/唔用 既consequence<br />\n二係呢2種情況既 consequence 二邊對比之下先得出結論 係咪真正環保<br />\n<br />\n問題係香港人點會認真去思考呢d 問題<br />\n單係第一點諗consequence 已經無人會做<br />\n佢地所謂環保只係用來打卡po IG 呃光環咋<br />\n同埋買下環保杯環保飯盒等自己又有藉口shopping <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點會理你係咪真係work<br />\n所以香港環保永遠係停係最低技術既層面: 用少d，唔好用，理撚得你係咪有需要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f0180f45b53295d15d07de683eab96876b5dc46","tid":864382,"uid":42246,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T07:49:36.000Z","msg":"好簡單 環保人士唔著衫 唔食肉 唔搭車 唔用手機<br />\n就係真環保 做到先再講野"},{"pid":"094c8f6d0bc96bc6e3b0b69782c9308e6fbe9fc7","tid":864382,"uid":17866,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"9f0180f45b53295d15d07de683eab96876b5dc46","tid":864382,"uid":42246,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T07:49:36.000Z","msg":"好簡單 環保人士唔著衫 唔食肉 唔搭車 唔用手機<br />\n就係真環保 做到先再講野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T07:56:01.000Z","msg":"環保人士死撚曬佢咪對地球最有益<br />\n學佢地講，源頭減廢嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e18dc79aa77ccae4f116cf43b53eb5f9e0c757d8","tid":864382,"uid":146923,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"66364737951a3188d02f5a720ae69fcd2fdcfd23","tid":864382,"uid":129235,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T07:48:56.000Z","msg":"樓主高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  正評<br />\n<br />\n留意一樣野，你講既3個例子全部都包含左2個步驟<br />\n<br />\n一係先評估 用/唔用 既consequence<br />\n二係呢2種情況既 consequence 二邊對比之下先得出結論 係咪真正環保<br />\n<br />\n問題係香港人點會認真去思考呢d 問題<br />\n單係第一點諗consequence 已經無人會做<br />\n佢地所謂環保只係用來打卡po IG 呃光環咋<br />\n同埋買下環保杯環保飯盒等自己又有藉口shopping <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點會理你係咪真係work<br />\n所以香港環保永遠係停係最低技術既層面: 用少d，唔好用，理撚得你係咪有需要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T07:57:36.000Z","msg":"啲人嘅著眼點淨係某啲物品嘅consumption volume<br />\n冇諗過disposal方面有好多嘢值得做、值得宣傳，一定比起叫你用少兩個膠袋來得有效。從根源解決問題，而唔係拿少兩支飲筒打兩張卡就成地精 點知令到個waste仲嚴重左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3fc7f6de4e7245b15074c09b8ccd52ddda98aa5","tid":864382,"uid":214883,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T07:58:40.000Z","msg":"講完一大論啲環保點冇用法, 咁你有冇咩好嘅實際嘅環保建議? 定咩都唔做最好? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bf01bbc23a3d230a89fe48809339cf0784b829b","tid":864382,"uid":146923,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c3fc7f6de4e7245b15074c09b8ccd52ddda98aa5","tid":864382,"uid":214883,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T07:58:40.000Z","msg":"講完一大論啲環保點冇用法, 咁你有冇咩好嘅實際嘅環保建議? 定咩都唔做最好? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T08:13:43.000Z","msg":"Subsidy<br />\n著眼多啲棄後處理嘅方法，正如我樓上咁講<br />\n同埋管好中國啲廠先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n正如你比幾隻老虎圍住 為左保命你唔會追住啲蚊嚟打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"200cdea8d10f4f5276a14f7bee957099e8773a3c","tid":864382,"uid":109136,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T08:18:25.000Z","msg":"樓主講得好<br />\n環保撚正正係只睇到眼前既野就算<br />\n<br />\n例子（一）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/13/174058_337d2d59c1d7ddf63d8139c211131adf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F13%2F174058_337d2d59c1d7ddf63d8139c211131adf.png&h=1392b319&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n自我感覺良好就夠？<br />\n咁你走個杯做乜鳩？<br />\n<br />\n例子（二）<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/13/174059_d93170b1db9f31a22890247cbdbf5b06.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.