\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWaNcKGw.png&h=d3d84087&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n派飯盒都要死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又話人地有責任<br />\n唔可以無左回事<br />\n<br />\n屌！係D 小店先會理鳩佢地"},{"pid":"cbf85d586b3575905440a67e15d0c48827e08c13","tid":864382,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T08:36:33.000Z","msg":"呢啲真係好on9"},{"pid":"7c52067b955203d2067f1abd267bb685267d0223","tid":864382,"uid":159448,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T08:36:38.000Z","msg":"環保吹我就識"},{"pid":"462f9caff0c7f90990d0029c77c142d4140edad9","tid":864382,"uid":82970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T08:37:22.000Z","msg":"正常都會倒瀉野，更何況老人家小朋友，食物浪費就好環保?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 飲管同個杯唔乾淨引起各種病痛 牙齒增加敏感同蛀牙等機會 各種資源就唔係浪費?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住堆環保撚: 個人問題 有病殘障睇醫生啦 又唔見我係咁 根本自私撚唔理個地球<br />\n<br />\n仆街啦屌你老母左膠思想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n已經有研究指出每年約有800 至 1100萬公頃海洋垃圾，當中只有2000公頃係飲管，換句話講連0.03%都冇，根本無視哂海龜以外既生物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 更加不願面對現實，去促請商家減排，隻眼開隻眼閉忽視更大既廢物來源同埋現時廢物處理既機制"},{"pid":"ea78b1ed9db62a9de62ac0268da832e55ba610fa","tid":864382,"uid":101328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c52067b955203d2067f1abd267bb685267d0223","tid":864382,"uid":159448,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T08:36:38.000Z","msg":"環保吹我就識"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T08:37:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07e4a3e4df2b6fdfcfabf7a9ca72264e36708345","t